00:33:32,019 --> 00:33:33,740
[SPEAKER_00] jer nemaš nikog vjernijeg od njega.

743
00:33:33,740 --> 00:33:34,960
[SPEAKER_00] Prevažno.

744
00:33:34,960 --> 00:33:36,240
[SPEAKER_00] Imat mir u srcu.

745
00:33:36,240 --> 00:33:38,299
[SPEAKER_00] Pričali smo o strahovima.

746
00:33:38,299 --> 00:33:40,279
[SPEAKER_00] Neće bit mirno srce

747
00:33:40,279 --> 00:33:41,240
[SPEAKER_00] ak si pun strahova

748
00:33:41,240 --> 00:33:43,059
[SPEAKER_00] i donosiš odluku i straha i emocije.

749
00:33:43,059 --> 00:33:44,559
[SPEAKER_00] Neće bit mirno.

750
00:33:44,559 --> 00:33:46,079
[SPEAKER_00] Zato, kaže,

751
00:33:46,079 --> 00:33:47,500
[SPEAKER_00] bolje predkazuje

752
00:33:47,500 --> 00:33:49,819
[SPEAKER_00] nego sedam stražara

753
00:33:49,819 --> 00:33:51,059
[SPEAKER_00] svi dikoca visokog.

754
00:33:51,859 --> 00:33:53,180
[SPEAKER_00] Bog je u tvoje srce

755
00:33:53,180 --> 00:33:54,380
[SPEAKER_00] utisno sve te želje

756
00:33:54,380 --> 00:33:56,240
[SPEAKER_00] i one odgađanjem samo rastu.

757
00:33:56,240 --> 00:34:00,759
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, dvije kvačice.

758
00:34:00,759 --> 00:34:03,140
[SPEAKER_00] Pobožnik, duhovnik, savjetnik.

759
00:34:03,140 --> 00:34:05,099
[SPEAKER_00] Druga kvačica, mir u srcu.

760
00:34:05,099 --> 00:34:06,519
[SPEAKER_00] Potpuni mir u srcu

761
00:34:06,519 --> 00:34:08,019
[SPEAKER_00] da u tom smjeru trebate ići.

762
00:34:08,019 --> 00:34:08,880
[SPEAKER_00] I treća stvar,

763
00:34:08,880 --> 00:34:10,820
[SPEAKER_00] ali se kraj svega toga

764
00:34:10,820 --> 00:34:12,099
[SPEAKER_00] moli svevišnjem

765
00:34:12,099 --> 00:34:13,800
[SPEAKER_00] da te vodi stazom istine.

766
00:34:13,800 --> 00:34:16,659
[SPEAKER_00] Natopi sve to dobro molitvom.

767
00:34:16,659 --> 00:34:18,820
[SPEAKER_00] U molitvi će ono se dogoditi

768
00:34:18,820 --> 00:34:20,699
[SPEAKER_00] što je Frastjepan govorio

769
00:34:20,699 --> 00:34:21,960
[SPEAKER_00] svjetlo će doći.

770
00:34:21,960 --> 00:34:23,820
[SPEAKER_00] Svjetlo dolazi.

771
00:34:23,820 --> 00:34:26,059
[SPEAKER_00] Rastlijetit će i tvoje nakane srca.

772
00:34:26,059 --> 00:34:28,500
[SPEAKER_00] Dogodit će se čudesni interventi Boži

773
00:34:28,500 --> 00:34:31,119
[SPEAKER_00] zato što Bog je tvoj otac

774
00:34:31,119 --> 00:34:34,199
[SPEAKER_00] koji želi biti dio tvojog životnog hoda,

775
00:34:34,199 --> 00:34:35,380
[SPEAKER_00] koji te ljubi.

776
00:34:35,380 --> 00:34:37,260
[SPEAKER_00] Ne raduje se tvoje grešci

777
00:34:37,260 --> 00:34:38,119
[SPEAKER_00] i tvoje pogrešci

778
00:34:38,119 --> 00:34:40,280
[SPEAKER_00] i želi da doneseš ispravne odluke.

779
00:34:40,280 --> 00:34:43,179
[SPEAKER_00] I zato nemoj ti kontrolirati

780
00:34:43,179 --> 00:34:44,119
[SPEAKER_00] svoju odluku

781
00:34:44,119 --> 00:34:45,960
[SPEAKER_00] nego mu propusti svoje staze.

782
00:34:45,960 --> 00:34:46,400
[SPEAKER_00] Amen.

783
00:34:50,699 --> 00:34:54,000
[UNKNOWN] Hvala što pratite kanal.

